Changes made in this release of OTDB
------------------------------------

The VICnodedef table is extended with one field:
ALTER TABLE VICnodeDef
    ADD COLUMN parentID INT4 NOT NULL DEFAULT 0;

ALTER TABLE vicnodedef
   DROP CONSTRAINT vnodedef_name_uniq;
ALTER TABLE vicnodedef
   ADD CONSTRAINT Vnodedef_name_uniq  UNIQUE(name, version, classif, parentID);


The new C++ class is: 
class VICNodeDef {
    nodeIDType      itsNodeID;
>>> nodeIDType      itsParentID;
    string          name;
    int32           version;
    int16           classif;
    string          constraints;
    string          description;

}


The affected functions are:
saveVCnode (authToken, nodeID, PARENTID, name, version, classif, constraints, description)

getVCNodeList_func : getVCNodeList --> Modified internally.
getVICnodeDef_func : getVICnodedef --> Modified internally.


buildTemplateTree_func : instanciateVTsubTree -> name/version
create_VIC_tables: --> add parentID ot VICnodedef table change index.
instanciateTree_func : resolveVHparam --> uses getVicnodedef (prev line)

The interface of the last 2 functions are changed:

